在使用过程中遇到了几个问题：&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>金才计划培训中的收获和感想</title><link>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/%E9%87%91%E6%89%8D%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E5%9F%B9%E8%AE%AD%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/</link><pubDate>Fri, 16 Jul 2021 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>itboyer@qq.com (iTBoyer)</author><guid>https://it-boyer.github.io/post/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/%E9%87%91%E6%89%8D%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E5%9F%B9%E8%AE%AD%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/</guid><description>&lt;div class="ox-hugo-toc toc"&gt;
